text: Sławomir Cieślakowski (born 2 May 1961) is a Polish rower. He competed in the men's quadruple sculls event at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:Polish male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Poland Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Warsaw
